<section
    class="relative w-full min-h-[60vh] flex flex-col justify-center p-4 md:p-12 pt-32 bg-[#0a0a0a] text-[#f0f0f0] overflow-hidden border-b border-[#333]"
>
    <div
        class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-20 pointer-events-none bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,#333_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:20px_20px]"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-start pt-20">
        <span class="text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.2em] text-[#666] uppercase mb-4"> v.2025 </span>
        <h1
            class="text-[10vw] leading-[0.8] font-bold tracking-tighter uppercase mix-blend-difference"
        >
            Escenario
            <span class="block text-[#333] stroke-text">Código</span>
            <span class="block text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#fff] to-[#666]"
                >Obra</span
            >
        </h1>
    </div>

    <div
        class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-20 border-t border-[#333] pt-8"
    >
        <div class="md:col-span-2">
            <p class="text-xl md:text-3xl font-light leading-tight text-[#ccc] max-w-3xl">
                Charlas que van más allá de la sintaxis. Reflexiones sobre ingeniería, producto y la
                responsabilidad de crear software que importa.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-end items-start md:items-end">
            <div
                class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-[#fff] flex items-center justify-center animate-spin-slow"
            >
                <svg
                    width="24"
                    height="24"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                >
                    <path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14"></path>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <style>
        .stroke-text {
            -webkit-text-stroke: 2px #333;
            color: transparent;
        }
        .animate-spin-slow {
            animation: spin 10s linear infinite;
        }
        @keyframes spin {
            from {
                transform: rotate(0deg);
            }
            to {
                transform: rotate(360deg);
            }
        }
    </style>
</section>
